summary: In this blog post, I share my hands-on experience comparing three coding agent harnesses: Codex, cmux + OpenCode, and Cursor. I break down their features, workspace management, notification systems, automation capabilities, and open source status, highlighting what sets each apart. Curious which harness might boost your productivity or fit your workflow best? Read on to find out!
